      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 12:51:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国政府在提前大选前大幅下调 2025 年经济预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/german-government-slashes-growth-forecast-before-snap-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国政府将今年的经济增长预期从 1.1% 下调至 0.3%，这是欧洲最大经济体仍陷入长期停滞的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/german-government-slashes-growth-forecast-before-snap-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 12:26:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
